      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i'm flying into heathrow tomorrow and need to get to edinburgh. i was thinking of taking the heathrow express to kings cross then switching to an lner train. what kind of buffer should i leave between the heathrow express getting in and the lner train leaving so i don't miss it? especially if the station is busy",
